<p>'Also huge congrats to <?php echo e('@'); ?>louisekielycasting, you're incredible, and also Sally and Alice and <?php echo e('@'); ?>element_pictures, we smashed it.'</p>

<p>Paul was quick to react to the tribute as he sweetly revealed he was 'weeping' over the surprise news. </p>

<p>He put: 'You are the best person. Properly weeping x.'</p>

<p>Daisy and Paul have won huge critical acclaim and the hearts of fans across the world for their portrayal of Maianne and Connell in the adaptation of Sally Rooney's 2018 novel of the same name. </p>

<p>Normal People was recently revealed to be the most watched show on BBC Three ever, with the first episode of the drama being watched by 6.75 million devices just two months after it aired. </p>
